Thank you for using the Incro Drinking Game App! This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use the app, particularly regarding third-party advertising.

**1. Data Collection:**
   - Incro does not collect personal information, including but not limited to names, email addresses, or location data.

**2. Third-Party Advertising:**
   - The app contains third-party advertising. These ads may collect information about your interests to present you with relevant ads. Please note that the privacy practices of these third-party providers are not controlled by us.

**3. Ad Providers:**
   - Advertising in Incro is provided by third-party ad networks. These networks may collect information about your app usage to display personalized ads.

**4. Opt-out:**
   - You can disable personalized advertising in your device settings. However, please note that this may impact the display of ad-supported content.

**5. No Personal Data in Ads:**
   - We do not transmit personal information to third-party ad networks to personalize ads.

**6. Changes to this Privacy Policy:**
   - This Privacy Policy may be updated occasionally to reflect changes in the app or our privacy practices. The current version of the Privacy Policy will be published on this page, with the date of the last update accordingly.

**7. Contact:**
   - If you have any questions or concerns regarding our privacy practices, you can contact us at incropartyspiel@gmail.com.

We hope you enjoy the Incro app and appreciate your trust.
